<!--
FIGURE OF GRAND SPIN AS FOLLOWS:

    Sides will face as in Grand Square, back up 3 steps & turn on #4 step,
    go forward then dosado (YOU MUST DOSADO) then Star Thru, you are now the new Heads,

    Heads will Star Thru, then Spin the Top, then Star Thru,
    to end facing the vacated sides position,
    then take a good step forward & California Twirl & Face.
    Heads you are now the new Sides.

    Repeat 3 more times and you are home.

    The Heads and Sides are working at the same time as in Grand Square.
-->
